{"id": 232073124, "title": "Novo Nordisk Boss on Ozempic and Eating Disorder Criticism, Social Media Pressure", "text": "Novo Nordisk Boss on Ozempic and Eating Disorder Criticism, Social Media Pressure Novo Nordisk has revolutionized the weight loss market with its blockbuster diabetes and obesity drugs, Ozempic and Wegovy. Celebrities have helped their popularity soar. Elon Musk, Sharon Osborne and Chelsea Handler have all publicly talked about taking Ozempic or Wegovy and they've had further backing from Oprah Winfrey. It\u2019s a global phenomenon - reaching millions on platforms like TikTok. Speaking on Bloomberg\u2019s Leaders With Lacqua, Novo Nordisk CEO Lars Fruergaard J\u00f8rgensen discusses the challenges the company has faced on social media and why he thinks trust needs to be placed in the doctors prescribing their drugs. (Source: Bloomberg)", "summary": "<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMigQFodHRwczovL3d3dy5ibG9vbWJlcmcuY29tL25ld3MvdmlkZW9zLzIwMjQtMDYtMDkvbm92by1ub3JkaXNrLWJvc3Mtb24tb3plbXBpYy1hbmQtZWF0aW5nLWRpc29yZGVyLWNyaXRpY2lzbS1zb2NpYWwtbWVkaWEtcHJlc3N1cmXSAQA?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">Novo Nordisk Boss on Ozempic and Eating Disorder Criticism, Social Media Pressure</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color=\"#6f6f6f\">Bloomberg</font>", "url": "https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-09/novo-nordisk-boss-on-ozempic-and-eating-disorder-criticism-social-media-pressure", "image": "https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i4PrHg1qZ7YI/v3/1200x630.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-09 16:31:35", "author": "Emily Chang", "authors": ["Emily Chang"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "us", "sentiment": 0.38}